    public class Area
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    This class of objects represents geographic of administrative areas returned by the NDE2 Discovery web service.
    Author:
    filip
    See Also:
    DetailedArea} -- a version of the area that has slightly more data; you want this for the Ordnance Survey envelope., Serialized Form
